                "invention-title": [
                    "Reactor and dehydrogenation device thereof",
                    "反应堆及其除氢装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The embodiment of the invention relates to a general chemical or physical method carried out in the presence of fluid, in particular to a reactor and a hydrogen removal device thereof. The reactor comprises a secondary loop, the hydrogen removal device is arranged in the secondary loop to remove hydrogen from the secondary loop, and the hydrogen removal device comprises a hydrogen removal device body, a hydrogen removal film, a first pipeline, a first hydrogen trap, a second pipeline, a second hydrogen trap and a metal steam filtering device. Liquid metal flows through the hydrogen removal film in the hydrogen removal device body to complete hydrogen removal. The first pipeline can vacuumize the hydrogen removal film and enable the hydrogen to flow out through the first pipeline; the first hydrogen trap collects hydrogen flowing out of the first pipeline; the second pipeline sucks out gas in the hydrogen removal device main body, the gas flows through the second hydrogen trap to collect hydrogen after metal steam is filtered by the metal steam filtering device, and the gas flowing out of the second hydrogen trap flows back to the hydrogen removal device main body. According to the hydrogen removal device provided by the embodiment of the invention, hydrogen in the liquid metal can be captured, and the purity of the liquid metal is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请的实施例涉及在有流体的情况下所进行的一般化学或物理的方法，具体涉及一种反应堆及其除氢装置。反应堆包括二回路，除氢装置设置在二回路对其除氢，除氢装置包括：除氢装置主体、除氢膜、第一管路、第一氢捕集器、第二管路、第二氢捕集器以及金属蒸汽过滤装置。液态金属流经除氢装置主体内部的除氢膜完成除氢；第一管路可将除氢膜抽真空并让氢气经第一管路流出；第一氢捕集器收集第一管路流出的氢气；第二管路将除氢装置主体内的气体吸出，气体经金属蒸汽过滤装置过滤金属蒸汽后，流经第二氢捕集器收集氢气，第二氢捕集器流出的气体流回至除氢装置主体。本申请的实施例提供的除氢装置能够捕集液态金属中的氢，提高液态金属的纯度。"
                }
            ]
